            "title": "Top 10 IT Companies in Noida",
            "content_html": "\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Noida is a newly formed hub of the IT sector since more and more IT companies are setting their operations up there. The IT corridor that is nestled in Noida has paved the way for a spectrum of job opportunities. Choosing a company that suits your needs and skills among a myriad of choices is hard and is a life-changing decision. But we are here to help you decide. The coming of IT companies in Noida has proved to be a boon for the economy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-information-technology-in-india\"><strong>Information Technology in India</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Information Technology in India is currently a thriving worldwide business, with India&#8217;s IT exports totalling approximately $70 billion with 2.8 million people employed in the field. According to the report, the IT Industry has become one of the country&#8217;s two leading industries.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-tata-companies-in-noida\"><strong>Tata Companies In Noida</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">On top of the list is tata consultancy services. TCS or Tata Consultancy Services is the largest Information Technology Company in India. They are a member of the Tata Group, India&#8217;s largest corporation. TCS is the world&#8217;s tenth-largest information technology service company in terms of revenue. TCS was founded in 1968 as a commercial subsidiary of Tata Sons Limited to provide information technology services to Tata Group companies. Punched card services for TISCO was their first assignment (Tata Steel). After that, TCS gradually began to take on projects outside of the Tata Group, and as a result of its rapid expansion, it quickly became the most sought-after IT firm in the country.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">TCS now has 67 branches across the world. They have 289 offices in 46 different countries. They have 147 delivery facilities spread throughout 21 nations. They work with clients from nearly every continent, including Forbes 500 companies.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">They employ the country&#8217;s greatest number of private-sector workers, with a total of 3,87,000 professionals of various nationalities. They employ about 3 lakh people in India alone. TCS has received several accolades on a variety of world-renowned venues. According to the top 20 rankings of Indian IT companies, TCS is placed first. TCS UK &amp; Ireland just received &#8216;Company of the Year&#8217; and &#8216;Social Responsibility Project of the Year&#8217; in 2016. This company is headquartered in Mumbai, India.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-noida-addresses-of-tcs\"><strong>Noida Addresses of TCS:</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Block A,</strong> <strong>Sector 62, Noida,</strong> <strong>Uttar Pradesh 201309</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Block A,</strong> <strong>Sector 63, Noida, 201301</strong> <strong>&nbsp;</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Unitech Building, Noida, Sector 135, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201304</strong><strong></strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Sector 80, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201305</strong><strong></strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-infosys\"><strong>Infosys</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Infosys is a global leader in digital services since they help businesses through their digital transformation in more than 50 countries<strong>.&nbsp;</strong>They proficiently guide their customers through their digital journey with over four decades of expertise managing the systems and workings of multinational companies. Infosys accomplishes this by providing the organisation with an AI-powered core that helps in prioritizing change implementation. Infosys, an NYSE-listed multinational consulting, and IT services business with over 250k employees was founded in 1981. They have accelerated some of the main developments that have led to India&#8217;s emergence as the worldwide destination for software services talent. Infosys was the first Indian IT company listed on NASDAQ and pioneered the Global Delivery Model.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">This Bengaluru-based firm specializes in information technology, outsourcing, and business consultancy. In 2018, there was information that Infosys was expanding its Noida headquarters. The proposal called for a \u20b9750 crore investment in Phase 1.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-address-of-infosys\"><strong>Noida address of Infosys:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Sector 85, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201305</strong><strong></strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-microsoft\"><strong>Microsoft</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Microsoft is a major proponent of information technology and the world&#8217;s largest IT corporation. It is the originator of goods such as Microsoft Office and is listed on the Fortune 500 list of leading corporations. This name has had an impact on the lives of many generations all across the world. It aspires to reach billions more in the years ahead. It is the place where software/IT visionaries go. Those that wish to see their dreams become a reality.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-address-of-microsoft\"><strong>Noida address of Microsoft:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>The R&amp;D office, Film City, Sector 16A, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301</strong><strong></strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-niit-technologies\"><strong>NIIT Technologies</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">NIIT is a significant Skills and Talent Development Corporation that is building a labour pool to suit global industry&#8217;s demands. Due to its broad and comprehensive variety of talent development programs, the firm was founded in 1981 to assist the embryonic IT sector in handling its human resource issues and now ranks among the world&#8217;s leading training companies. NIIT&#8217;s learning and talent development solutions have been recognized worldwide for the fifth year in a row as India&#8217;s Most Trusted Training Brand (Brand Trust Report, 2017). Financial and banking institutions, insurance, travel and transportation are just a few of the industries that NIIT Technologies services. It was formed in 2004 and had its headquarters in Noida. It also has a presence in 18 different nations.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-addresses-of-niit\"><strong>Noida addresses of NIIT:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>SEZ Developer Unit</strong> <strong>Sector Tech Zone,</strong> <strong>Noida, UP 201308</strong> <strong>Ph: +91 (120) 459 2300</strong> <strong>&nbsp;</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Sector 63, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301</strong><strong></strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-cadence\"><strong>Cadence</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Cadence Design was formed in 1988 when SDA Systems and EACD merged to form Cadence Design. Design Services, Training, Hosted Design Solutions, Methodology Services, and Virtual Integrated Computer-Aided Design are some of the services they provide (VCAD). They have four distribution hubs in India, located in Pune, Bangalore, Hyderabad, and Noida. Their India headquarters are in Noida, Uttar Pradesh, and it is one of the company&#8217;s major offices.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-address-of-cadence\"><strong>Noida address of cadence</strong>:</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Noida Special Economic Zone, Phase-2, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201305</strong> &nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-adobe\"><strong>Adobe</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Adobe is the world&#8217;s leading provider of digital media and marketing solutions. As a result, everyone \u2013 from fledgling artists to major companies \u2013 can use their creative, marketing, and document solutions to bring digital ideas to life and deliver immersive, engaging experiences to the right person at the right time for the greatest outcomes. In a nutshell, Adobe is everywhere, and they are transforming the world with digital technology. Adobe specializes in multimedia, creative, and digital media tools. Adobe&#8217;s products include Adobe Flash, Adobe PDF, Adobe Photoshop, and others.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-address-of-adobe\"><strong>Noida Address of Adobe:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Vindhyachal Marg, Sector 25A, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Noida-Greater Noida Expy, Sector 132, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201304</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-oracle\"><strong>Oracle</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Oracle, based in Austin, Texas, is an American multinational computer technology business. Database software and technology, cloud designed systems, and enterprise software solutions are all sold by the firm, including its own database management systems. Oracle was the world&#8217;s second-largest software business in terms of sales and market capitalization in 2020. Oracle creates, produces, and sells both software and hardware and services to go along with it (such as financing, training, consulting, and hosting services). Oracle&#8217;s product range has grown significantly as a result of acquisitions. Oracle has a global footprint as well.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-address-of-oracle\"><strong>Noida address of oracle:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Lotus Business Park, Tower A, Express Highway, Sector 127, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Express Trade Tower, 2, Noida-Greater Noida Expy, Sector 132, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201304</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Sector 2, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-hcl-technologies\"><strong>HCL Technologies</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">HCL is the largest company in Noida, with ten offices. HCL, which was founded in 1976, is a major IT company that serves a number of Fortune 100 companies across the world. Application Services, BPO, Engineering and R&amp;D Services, and Infrastructure Management Services are their major service offerings in the Manufacturing, Finance, Healthcare &amp; Life Sciences, Retail, Telecom, and Media industries. They have operations in 34 countries throughout the world, with their headquarters in Noida.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">&#8221; Ideapreneurship&#8221; is created by HCL. An Ideapreneur is a person who takes responsibility for their concept, transforms it into reality, and develops a solution that propels the organisation ahead. HCL&#8217;s engine is its intrapreneurs. The self-sustaining, self-inspired innovation engine that propels HCL ahead is ideapreneurship. It is a one-of-a-kind innovation culture in which every employee is encouraged to think outside the box and where everyday ideas help to shape a new business paradigm.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-addresses-of-hcl\"><strong>Noida addresses of HCL:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>Sector 60, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>SW Tower 1 HCL Technologies, Sector 126, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201303</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>Sector 3, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201307</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Technology Hub Sector 126 SEZ, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201303</strong><strong></strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-grapecity\"><strong>GrapeCity</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">GrapeCity is a Japanese information technology firm with operations in Japan, India, Vietnam, China, and the United States. Their India office is at Sector 62, Noida. They were once known as Bunka Orient until changing their name to GrapeCity in 2002. They specialise in customized software development, syndicated product development, IT Consulting Services, and Customer Relations.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-address-of-grapecity\"><strong>Noida address of GrapeCity:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>&nbsp;<strong>Sector 62, Okhla Industrial Development Area, Uttar Pradesh,201307</strong> &nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-wipro-limited\"><strong>Wipro Limited</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">Wipro has its headquarters in Bangalore, and it is a prominent provider of information technology services. In the year 2013, the firm decided to focus on its business and separate it from the rest of its divisions. The firm has a long history of invention and entrepreneurship. However, it is now reversing its strategy to capitalise on the promise of digital technologies such as artificial intelligence and cloud computing. Wipro employs approximately 190,000 people on six continents to serve our clients. We uncover new ideas and connect the connections to create a better and more ambitious future.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-noida-address-of-wipro\"><strong>Noida address of Wipro:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>&nbsp;Plot no A1 &#8211; Sec 3, Noida &#8211; 201301, Uttar Pradesh</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">These are 10 of the best IT companies in Noida based on various ratings by current and former employees. But there is no need to get anxious if you did not find the one you were looking for. These are just a fraction of the IT companies in Noida. There are many options to choose from.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-conclusion\"><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">India&#8217;s IT sector is anticipated to grow at a pace of 12 to 14 per cent in 2016-2017. India&#8217;s economy demands more hardware, software, as well as other IT services. This clearly demonstrates that information technology is a sector that will likely be one of the rising industries in the future. India has been a popular location for IT outsourcing. One of the most significant advantages of the computer and information technology business in India is the potential for job creation. In India, there are plenty of IT employment openings. In fact, India is anticipated to surpass the United States as the country with the most software developers in 2018 (52 lakh vs 42 lakh in the United States).</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-you-might-also-like\">You Might Also Like</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-yoast-seo-related-links\"><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/tcs-set-lease-8-lakh-sq-ft-office-space-chennai-one-sez\">TCS set to lease 8 lakh sq ft of office space in Chennai One SEZ</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/top-it-companies-in-mumbai\">Top IT companies in Mumbai</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/tata-housing-comes-up-with-fixed-interest-rates-on-home-loans-for-buyers\">Tata Housing comes up with fixed interest rates on home loans for buyers</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/bhulekh-uttar-pradesh\">Bhulekh Uttar Pradesh: Online Land Records Portal of UP</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.squareyards.com/blog/investing-in-sector-90-noida\">Investing in Sector 90 Noida</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-frequently-asked-questions-faqs\">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>\n\n\n        <section class=\"sc_fs_faq sc_card\">\n            <div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2>What are the best-paying Software and IT companies in Noida?</h2>         